HEADWORD: Blancmanger
<hw>Blanc*man"ger</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. See
<er>Blancmange</er>.]</ety> <def>A sort of fricassee with white sauce,
variously made of capon, fish, etc.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
